ol.li: A CDN is made up of a hierarchy of Tenants up to 10 layers
Each Tenant can only have one parent Tenant
Each Tenant can be assigned many child Tenants
Each Tenant can be assigned many Services
Each Service is assigned to only one Tenant
Each Tenant can be assigned many Users
Each User is assigned to at least one Tenant
Each User may be assigned to many Tenants
Users inherit access to all child Tenants and Services below the Tenant they are assigned
